00:53:29.090 --> 00:53:32.273
Netting is it it is basically--

00:53:32.273 --> 00:53:33.440
again, with cash instrument.

00:53:33.440 --> 00:53:34.857
I'm not talking
about derivatives.

00:53:34.857 --> 00:53:36.710
Derivatives is a
different issue.

00:53:36.710 --> 00:53:38.330
With cash instruments,
the only reason

00:53:38.330 --> 00:53:39.410
why you have
counterparty risk is

00:53:39.410 --> 00:53:41.610
because it's not clear--
