00:56:14.290 --> 00:56:15.290
GARY GENSLER: You could.

00:56:15.290 --> 00:56:15.920
Absolutely.

00:56:15.920 --> 00:56:19.250
AUDIENCE: I mean, you
still keep this system

00:56:19.250 --> 00:56:23.210
that people are
