But it has to be done before
you move the settlement.

00:59:18.380 --> 00:59:21.140
And that's what's
called clearing.

00:59:21.140 --> 00:59:24.080
So it's a question of whether
you have simultaneous execution

00:59:24.080 --> 00:59:28.130
