01:07:47.750 --> 01:07:51.140
on private securities,
which were not--

01:07:51.140 --> 01:07:53.420
they certainly weren't liquid.

01:07:53.420 --> 01:07:55.790
I don't know enough about
what they did there as

01:07:55.790 --> 01:07:58.370
to how illiquid they were.

01:07:58.370 --> 01:08:03.380
But they felt, all right, this
