01:16:16.700 --> 01:16:17.627
Right?

01:16:17.627 --> 01:16:18.960
GARY GENSLER: I agree with that.

01:16:18.960 --> 01:16:21.190
We're still very much
at the early days.

01:16:21.190 --> 01:16:24.210
But I think this is an
interesting, real, live thing.

01:16:24.210 --> 01:16:27.100
